{"tid":2178651,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【檢測碼商業應用】的士業界推計劃 檢測呈陰性司機可在車廂展示結果","createTime":"2020-08-28T13:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T08:19:23.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"5c51c1ea353fa734773343f0c4e35018e39b586e","tid":2178651,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:37:16.000Z","msg":"的士業界推計劃 檢測呈陰性司機可在車廂展示結果<br />\n<br />\n運輸署鼓勵的士司機，積極參與下周二起的普及社區檢測計劃，指業界並會推出「的士司機抗疫檢測名牌」計劃，讓在檢測計劃取得陰性短訊報告的司機，在的士車廂內當眼位置展示，讓乘客知悉。名牌會顯示司機姓名、司機證編號及收到陰性檢測結果的日期<br />\n<br />\n運輸署表示，領取名牌屬自願性質、費用全免及無需預約，有意參與的司機，可以到30多個指定的士團體，經核對資料後領取名牌，署方稍後會在網頁公布協助派發檢測名牌的士團體名單、地址、辦公日期及時間。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2354732\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2354732&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyMLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=a5e5c1da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2354732</a>"},{"pid":"d0989c34bf90d31e4b8b66a60b4dccd8367b9b53","tid":2178651,"uid":77717,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:37:57.000Z","msg":"有認證真好"},{"pid":"1184d148b88609a375b0ea1beabf2a247e6282d6","tid":2178651,"uid":22556,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:38:34.000Z","msg":"邊個講一日陰性 就永遠陰性架！<br />\n你由去檢驗嗰一刻就已經有確診嘅風險"},{"pid":"b1662e05a295f98be889bb61d7ceb3fbfc8d46ce","tid":2178651,"uid":183758,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"5c51c1ea353fa734773343f0c4e35018e39b586e","tid":2178651,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:37:16.000Z","msg":"的士業界推計劃 檢測呈陰性司機可在車廂展示結果<br />\n<br />\n運輸署鼓勵的士司機，積極參與下周二起的普及社區檢測計劃，指業界並會推出「的士司機抗疫檢測名牌」計劃，讓在檢測計劃取得陰性短訊報告的司機，在的士車廂內當眼位置展示，讓乘客知悉。名牌會顯示司機姓名、司機證編號及收到陰性檢測結果的日期<br />\n<br />\n運輸署表示，領取名牌屬自願性質、費用全免及無需預約，有意參與的司機，可以到30多個指定的士團體，經核對資料後領取名牌，署方稍後會在網頁公布協助派發檢測名牌的士團體名單、地址、辦公日期及時間。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2354732\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2354732&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyMLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=a5e5c1da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2354732</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:39:00.000Z","msg":"有呢個碼先唔敢搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573d580e53d2ebab516468c492dbd4b02358bb57","tid":2178651,"uid":295602,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:39:07.000Z","msg":"個的士司機show佢驗嗰陣陰性<br />\n但係本身的士就係會周圍去, 佢個人食飯又會周圍去, 佢又會周圍接載唔同人<br />\n<br />\n咁成個&quot;應用&quot;有乜撚野用?"},{"pid":"7d65517989108ac5b9931e077191b8b3830574aa","tid":2178651,"uid":312598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:39:43.000Z","msg":"個名牌有抗病毒功能?"},{"pid":"af4887509e8d6ddc90bbddbcf3c8b9e94a0d180c","tid":2178651,"uid":304281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:40:07.000Z","msg":"的士佬on9都唔係第一日<br />\n上得車就驚條鐵咩"},{"pid":"5c4e20f83e38c04662b2dcb48e53dee7b82544e5","tid":2178651,"uid":263618,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53e970e70fb5170c4a8d2330cc4a88d6e89c3496","tid":2178651,"uid":120123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:40:30.000Z","msg":"開始搞小動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c4d43426f3c604ce0a4468f57e91a27a405e26","tid":2178651,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:40:48.000Z","msg":"好似同人講<br />\n<br />\n歡迎您中出"},{"pid":"2c4c0506b55e23f6e77ff83cdff894454af0d642","tid":2178651,"uid":71215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:41:48.000Z","msg":"此地無銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7bcd9dadb1b418f6d639d12fe80294945f457de